          <div class="callout-label">Watch for these red flags</div>
          <p>Avoid any tool that <strong>(a)</strong> requires you to "learn SEO" before you can use it, <strong>(b)</strong> charges $300+ for a tier called "Small Business" (that is enterprise pricing in disguise), or <strong>(c)</strong> locks you into an annual contract before you have published a single article. Monthly billing should be the default.</p>
        </div>

